Annotations used by extensions to provide information about their configuration fields.

See:
          Description

Annotation Types Summary
AcceptorsList Used to annotate an acceptor or a collection of acceptors.
ConnectorsList Used to annotate a connector or a collection of connectors.
Label Specifies a custom label for the field.
List  
Required Tells that the field is required.
 

Package org.mokai.ui.annotation Description

Annotations used by extensions to provide information about their configuration fields. GUI's can use this information to render the fields and for input validation.
